0 \- read name (string)
.
.IP "\(bu" 4
1 \- flag (integer)
.
.IP "\(bu" 4
2 \- reference sequence ID (integer)
.
.IP "\(bu" 4
3 \- 1\-based leftmost mapping position (integer)
.
.IP "\(bu" 4
