.
.IP "\(bu" 4
9 \- template length (integer)
.
.IP "\(bu" 4
10 \- segment sequence (string)
.
.IP "\(bu" 4
11 \- phred\-base quality (array of integers)
.
.IP "\(bu" 4
12 \- tags (map : string \-> value)
.
.IP "" 0
.
.P
